= RELEASE HISTORY

== 1.1.0 / 2009-08-14

This release brings some nice improements to Pom, in
particular the addition of the Project class and it's
supporting classes History and Manifest, which were
taken and deprecated from Reap.

* 3 Major Enhancements

    * Metadata is loaded passively as needed.
    * Metadata fallback is parsed README.
    * Project class has added, taken from Reap.

== 1.0.0 / 2009-07-22

This is the initial release of POM.

* 1 Major Enhancment

    * Happy Birthday!

